## 2. Methodology

### üõ† Tools & Techniques
```sql
-- Example of analytical techniques used
SELECT
    YEAR(order_date) AS year,
    SUM(sales) AS revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) AS customers
FROM fact_refined_sales_details
GROUP BY YEAR(order_date);
